scriptLines:
query: 'SELECT User_Id, 
       First_Name, 
       Last_Name, 
       Email_Address, 
       Termination_Flag, 
       Department_Name, 
       NPN_Grouping, 
       Upline_Id,
       Upline_First_Name, 
       Upline_Last_Name, 
       Level_Seq, 
       MAX(Record_Load_date) AS Max_Record_Load_date
FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_AGENCY_EMP_HIER_DETAILS_HISTORY] AS emp
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_AGENCY_PAYEE_DETAILS] AS payee
    WHERE payee.Employee_ID = emp.USER_ID
)
GROUP BY User_Id, 
         First_Name, 
         Last_Name, 
         Email_Address, 
         Termination_Flag, 
         Department_Name, 
         NPN_Grouping, 
         Upline_Id,
         Upline_First_Name, 
         Upline_Last_Name, 
         Level_Seq',

query: 'Select 
E2EIS_SEQ_NUMBER,CARRIER,AGENCY_NAME,AGENCY_IDENTIFIER,AGENT_ID ASSIGNED_AGENT_NUMBER,AGENT_NPN,AGENT_FULL_NAME ASSIGNED_AGENT_NAME,PLAN_NAME,
PRODUCT,CONTRACT_ID Policy_id, CONTRACT_MEMBER_COUNT MEMBER_COUNT, MEMBER_RELATIOSHIP,MEMBER_FIRST_NAME SUBSCRIBER_FIRST_NAME,MEMBER_LAST_NAME SUBSCRIBER_LAST_NAME,
MEMBER_DOB SUBSCRIBER_DOB,COUNTY_NAME COUNTY,EXCHANGE_INDICATOR,PRIMARY_MEMBER_ID,PRODUCT_TYPE,BEST_AVAILABLE_POSTAL_CODE ZIP_CODE,
COVERAGE_EFFECTIVE_DATE COVERAGE_START_DATE,COVERAGE_EXPIRATION_DATE COVERAGE_END_DATE, AGENT_CONTRACT_START_DATE BROKER_START_DATE,AGENT_CONTRACT_TERM_DATE BROKER_END_DATE,
MEMBER_ORIGINAL_EFFECTIVE_DATE SUBSCRIBER_ORIGINAL_EFFECTIVE_DATE,CONTRACT_STATUS POLICY_STATUS,
MEMBER_PHONE_NUMBER MEMBER_PHONE_NUMBER_1, MEMBER_EMAIL_ADDRESS SUBSCRIBER_EMAIL,
ACTIVITY_FLAG,POLICY_RANK,
POLICY_ADDED_DATE,POLICY_RETENTION_DATE,POLICY_REMOVED_DATE,POLICY_CANCELLED_DATE,
POLICY_LAST_RECEIVED_DATE,PERIOD_NAME,PERIOD_DESCRIPTION,PERIOD_START_DATE,PERIOD_END_DATE,
BILL_STATUS,Original_Policy_Status,Policy_Reactivation_date,Adds_member_Count,Cancels_Member_Count,
MEMBER_RESPONSIBILITY,ACCOUNTINGDATE,COMPENSATION_TYPE Annual_Compensation_type, SUBSCRIBER_ORIG_EFFDATE_HIS AGENCY_SUBSCRIBER_ORIG_EFFDATE
from [SIM_103].SIM_BOOK_OF_BUSSINESS_ALL_CARRIERS_FB',

query: 'SELECT
    E2EIS_SEQ_NUMBER,
    CARRIER,
    OWNING_AGENT_OF_RECORD,
    ASSIGNED_AGENT_NUMBER,
    BROKER_START_DATE,
    BROKER_END_DATE,
    PRODUCT_TYPE,
    PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION,
    IMS_TRANSACTION_ID,
    POLICY_STATUS,
    POLICY_ID,
    GROUP_NAME,
    MEMBER_COUNT,
    [ON/OFF_EXCHANGE] AS ON_OFF_EXCHANGE,
    EXCHANGE_SUBSCRIBER_ID,
    COVERAGE_TYPE,
    SUBSCRIBER_ORIGINAL_EFFECTIVE_DATE,
    COVERAGE_START_DATE,
    COVERAGE_END_DATE,
    PAID_THROUGH_DATE,
    SUBSCRIBER_FIRST_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_MIDDLE_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_LAST_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_FULL_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_DOB,
    SUBSCRIBER_EMAIL,
    ADDRESS,
    ADDRESS_2,
    ZIP_CODE,
    CITY,
    STATE,
    COUNTY,
    APP_SUBMIT_DATE,
    MEMBER_PHONE_NUMBER_1,
    MEMBER_PHONE_NUMBER_2,
    COMPENSATION_TYPE,
    COMPENSATION_PERIOD,
    COMPENSATION_AMOUNT,
    PAYEE_NAME,
    MAIN_UPLINE_AGENT,
    GROUP_TEAM_SALES,
    TRANSITION_DATE,
    ASSIGNED_AGENT_NAME,
    AGENCY_ID,
    RECORD_LOAD_DATE,
    RECORD_LOADED_BY,
    RECORD_DATA_SOURCE,
    RECORD_FLAG_STATUS,
    COMMENTS,
    POLICY_ADDED_DATE,
    POLICY_REMOVED_DATE,
    POLICY_CANCELLED_DATE,
    POLICY_REACTIVATION_DATE,
    POLICY_RETENTION_DATE,
    ADDS_MEMBER_COUNT,
    CANCELS_MEMBER_COUNT,
    ORIGINAL_POLICY_STATUS,
    ACTIVITY_FLAG,
    Period_Start_date,
    Period_End_date,
    Period_Name,
    Period_Description,
    Bill_Status,
    AGENCY_SUBSCRIBER_ORIG_EFFDATE,
    AGENCY_SUBSCRIBER_ORIG_EFFDATE_HIS
FROM (
    SELECT *,
           ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
               ORDER BY
                   CARRIER ASC,
                   POLICY_ID ASC,
                   POLICY_STATUS ASC,
                   COVERAGE_START_DATE DESC
           ) AS rn
    FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_BOOK_OF_BUSSINESS_ALL_CARRIERS_JOINED]
) t',
